# Forge Council quality

Every milestone closure requires: acceptance coverage, touched files, validation executed or explicitly deferred with risk, rollback notes, doc impact, security notes, artifact completeness, resume implications.

Use `_system/VALIDATION_GATES.md`, `TEST_STRATEGY.md`, and `bootstrap/fc-gate-check.sh` when implementing gates.

Never claim tests passed without evidence in repo or run artifacts.
